{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":84,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"小孩","listener":"char_tie_xing_lao_ren","text":"大年初一，你不在家里，陪着孩子过年，跑到这里来瞪着我看什么？\n\n我有什么好看的？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":6,"line_start":36,"line_end":38},{"speaker":"char_tie_xing_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_li_huai","text":"你姓什么？","tone":"严肃","chapter":6,"line_start":42,"line_end":42},{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"小孩","listener":"char_tie_xing_lao_ren","text":"我不知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":6,"line_start":44,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_tie_xing_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_li_huai","text":"你不知道？原来你连自己姓什么都不知道。","tone":"疑问","chapter":6,"line_start":46,"line_end":46},{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"小孩","listener":"char_tie_xing_lao_ren","text":"为什么一定要知道？我没有爹没有娘没有姓，那是我家的事，跟你有什么狗屁关系，你凭什么问我？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":6,"line_start":48,"line_end":50},{"speaker":"char_tie_xing_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_li_huai","text":"你怎么知道跟我没关系？我到这里来，就是特地来找你的。","tone":"认真","chapter":6,"line_start":54,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"小孩","listener":"char_tie_xing_lao_ren","text":"找我？你又不认得我找我干吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":6,"line_start":56,"line_end":56},{"speaker":"char_tie_xing_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_li_huai","text":"我认得你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":6,"line_start":58,"line_end":58},{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"小孩","listener":"char_tie_xing_lao_ren","text":"你认得我？你怎么会认得我？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":6,"line_start":60,"line_end":60},{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"小孩","listener":"char_tie_xing_lao_ren","text":"你知道我是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":6,"line_start":62,"line_end":62},{"speaker":"char_tie_xing_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_li_huai","text":"我知道，我当然知道。","tone":"悲伤","chapter":6,"line_start":64,"line_end":64},{"speaker":"char_tie_xing_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_li_huai","text":"我也认得你的父亲，如果没有他，现在我就算活着没死也比你更惨。","tone":"悲痛","chapter":6,"line_start":66,"line_end":68},{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"小孩","listener":"char_tie_xing_lao_ren","text":"你是谁？你姓什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":6,"line_start":72,"line_end":72},{"speaker":"char_tie_xing_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_li_huai","text":"我姓铁。","tone":"陈述","chapter":6,"line_start":74,"line_end":74},{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"小孩","listener":"char_tie_xing_lao_ren","text":"那么我呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":6,"line_start":76,"line_end":76},{"speaker":"char_tie_xing_lao_ren","speaker_name":"老人","listener":"char_li_huai","text":"你姓李。你的名字应该叫李善。","tone":"悲伤","chapter":6,"line_start":78,"line_end":78},{"speaker":"char_li_huai","speaker_name":"小孩","listener":"char_tie_xing_lao_ren","text":"李善，我的名字应该叫李善，像我这么样的人，就算姓李，也应该叫李坏。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":6,"line_start":82,"line_end":83}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_li_huai","name":"李坏","alias":["李善"],"identity":"孤儿，李善之子","faction":"无","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"大年初一流落山城的倔强孤儿，拒绝接受施舍，天生不屈","personality":{"traits":["倔强","不屈","自尊心强","孤傲","叛逆","刚烈"],"speech_style":"直率粗犷，带脏字，语气凶巴巴","temperament":"刚烈不屈，宁死不受施舍"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_tie_xing_lao_ren","type":"初识","intensity":30,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"被老人找上门，得知身世"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[6],"source_refs":[{"chapter":6,"line_start":1,"line_end":84,"text":"整个章节描述小孩（李坏）在山城大年初一遇到银发老人，得知自己姓李名善"}]},{"id":"char_tie_xing_lao_ren","name":"铁姓老人","alias":["银发老人","老人"],"identity":"银发老者，认识李坏之父","faction":"无","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"满头银发的神秘老人，认识李坏的父亲，特地来找李坏告知身世","personality":{"traits":["严肃","沉痛","悲伤","神秘","威严","慈悲"],"speech_style":"严肃沉稳，语气充满悲伤","temperament":"沉痛而威严"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_li_huai","type":"初识","intensity":40,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"主动寻找并告知身世"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[6],"source_refs":[{"chapter":6,"line_start":32,"line_end":78,"text":"一个高大威猛，满头银发的老人突然出现在他面前，我姓铁。"}]},{"id":"cha